ToolLocationWhat it does
Zonal StatisticsZonal toolsetSummarizes values in a raster layer by zones (categories) in another layerâ€”for example, calculate the mean elevation for each vegetation category.
CombineLocal toolsetAssigns a value to each cell in the output layer based on unique combinations of values from several input layers.
Weighted OverlayOverlay toolsetAutomates the raster overlay process and lets you assign weights to each layer before adding (you can also specify equal influence to create an unweighted overlay).
Weighted SumOverlay toolsetOverlays several rasters, multiplying each by their given weight and summing them together.
